# use proper virt module commands, like: 

- name: manage libvirt guests 
  user: ansible 
  hosts: barelaptop

  tasks:
   - name: get list of vms
     virt: command=list_vms
     register: virt_vms

   - debug: var=virt_vms

For further info see: https://github.com/sfromm/ansible-playbooks/blob/master/virt-guests.yml

